    "description": {
      "zh": "军规6.8x51毫米（.277 FURY）步枪弹，拥有双重金属外壳（不锈钢与黄铜）。提供比5.56x45弹药更高的初速度和更多动能，同时比7.62x51具有更强的打击力，还能有效穿透现代防弹护甲。",
      "en": "A mil-spec 6.8x51mm (.277 FURY) rifle round with bi-metallic case (stainless steel base coupled to a brass body), manufactured by SIG Sauer. Provides a higher velocity, more energy hitting being transferred to the target, and a lighter cartridge than 5.56x45, and hits harder than 7.62x51, while also having a great penetration power against modern body armor."
    },
